Muchidzidzo che[[masvomhu]], '''hukuru''' (''Magnitude'') izwi rinotaura kukura kwakaita nhamba zvisinei kuti ine vara (-) kana (+) pamberi payo. Somuenzaniso, -50 ine hukuru hwakaenzana ne +50, nyangwe zvavo nhamba mbiri idzi dzakasiyana pahuwandu hwadzo; +50 yakawanda pane -50.

